Text:
Thank you for your regular updates with new KIS keys - please keep them coming.

Only 2 keys haven't already been blocked.

DAMNIT ALL! They got blocked! Seriously if I dont find a working key soon I just might go crazy... It seems like I have to get a new every 3 days...

Can someone just give me a key generator so I will be the only one using that particular unique key? That way it wont be blocked because of multiple clients attempting to use the key.
